item.title: Diary, 22nd April 2016
item.description: Always busy here! Aral and I have been doing a good job of getting out to events in our new home city of Malmö. Last week we went to see A Good American at DocLounge, and this week we’ve been to a few events right here in Media Evolution City. We’re really lucky to have an amazing venue that hosts so many events around us. I’ve been knuckling down on the financial/admin side of things now we’ve moved to Malmö.
